chess.logic.inputprocessing

Class InputProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • chess.logic.inputprocessing.InputProcessor

  • public class InputProcessor
extends Object
    This is responsible for connecting graphical user interface to other logic classes. Class offers methods update text given to players and process information given by graphical user interface to move pieces accordingly in game.

    sami
